    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras/756cc0d4e770cc1940a797ee3688adda.avif?t=1730409079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras_big/756cc0d4e770cc1940a797ee3688adda.avif?t=1730409079 width=800 height=387 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild Whiskers Café is an educational café simulator game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook meals and make smoothies for a wide range of wild customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras/da77bd6e05f039d173d2596f8c29e062.avif?t=1730409079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras_big/da77bd6e05f039d173d2596f8c29e062.avif?t=1730409079 width=800 height=822 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ Animal Customers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ Recipes to make!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your café!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about different animal species!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lofi Soundtrack!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras/ea30bf962ddda5c70f958b481bbf6f3d.avif?t=1730409079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras_big/ea30bf962ddda5c70f958b481bbf6f3d.avif?t=1730409079 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Two Gameplay Modes!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet different customers and learn about them! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new recipes &amp; decorate your café!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Food Truck Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-Paced cooking mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serve as many customers as possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras/dc9dd16af682dcf43246b136710a083a.avif?t=1730409079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240590/extras_big/dc9dd16af682dcf43246b136710a083a.avif?t=1730409079 width=800 height=597 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun Fact! The biggest land mammal known is believed to be Paraceratherium orgosensis! An ancient relative of the rhino, thought to be 4.8 metres / 15.7 feet tall, and 7.4 metres / 24.3 feet long!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
